Playing lookout for those gangsters.

139
00:08:07.285 --> 00:08:08.368
He's changed.

140
00:08:08.403 --> 00:08:10.037
He's not like that anymore.

141
00:08:12.490 --> 00:08:14.658
You got it bad. don't you?

142
00:08:14.709 --> 00:08:16.543
He's a good guy. Paz.

143
