188
00:10:10.235 --> 00:10:12.236
Do that.

189
00:10:19.494 --> 00:10:20.494
You see the triads?

190
00:10:20.496 --> 00:10:22.379
Yeah. and the Italians.

191
00:10:22.414 --> 00:10:24.048
