203
00:10:42.408 --> 00:10:43.742
Mmm.

204
00:10:43.776 --> 00:10:45.994
Man. I hate going out there.

205
00:10:46.029 --> 00:10:46.695
You're driving.

206
00:10:46.728 --> 00:10:47.728
Come on.

207
00:10:47.779 --> 00:10:48.896
