234
00:11:54.879 --> 00:11:56.463
All right. look.

235
00:11:56.514 --> 00:11:59.967
Barring a huge development
in your Lobos investigation.

236
00:11:59.969 --> 00:12:01.518
I'm gonna need your answer about Detroit

237
00:12:01.552 --> 00:12:02.936
