387
00:18:48.759 --> 00:18:50.877
Nope.

388
00:18:50.928 --> 00:18:54.381
No?

389
00:18:54.432 --> 00:18:56.433
Isabela. mi amor...

390
00:18:56.531 --> 00:18:57.831
_

